data.description: Welcome to your new home located on a cul-de-sac just minutes from Lake Zorinsky! This 4 bedroom, 3 bath home is the epitome of comfort and functionality. The sun-drenched front living room boasts abundant natural light. Cozy up on chilly evenings by the fireplace, embraced by the charm of built-in bookcases. The allure of this home continues as you explore the spacious bedrooms, each offering a haven of tranquility and privacy. Stepping down into the finished basement, a world of possibilities unfolds with an entertainment area as well as two additional rooms perfect for workout area and/or office space. The backyard is fully fenced to ensure privacy and safety. In addition this gem comes complete with a 2-car garage with plenty of storage space. Convenience is key here, with all appliances included – just pack your bags and move right in!
